\begin_layout Standard
它在试验时, 把试点安排在黄金分割点上来寻找最佳点.
 而生产生活中, 我们常常取其近似值0.618, 因此得名.
 0.618法是最常用的单因素单峰目标函数优选法之一.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设因素范围为
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

, 取第一试点第二试点
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $x_{2}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $x_{2}<x_{1}$
\end_inset

, 且
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $x_{2}$
\end_inset

 关于
\begin_inset Formula $[a,b]$
\end_inset

的中心对称,即
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}-a=x_{2}-b$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果
\begin_inset Formula $x_{1}$
\end_inset

是好点,
\begin_inset Formula $x_{2}$
\end_inset

是差点, 于是舍去
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{1},b]$
\end_inset

,再在存优范围内进行重复实验.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如果要求每次按比例舍去:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{b-x_{1}}{b-a}=\frac{x_{1}-x_{2}}{x_{1}-a}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
变形得:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $1-\frac{b-x_{1}}{b-a}=1-\frac{x_{1}-x_{2}}{x_{1}-a}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{x_{1}-a}{b-a}=\frac{x_{2}-a}{x_{1}-a}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{x_{1}-a}{b-a}=1-t$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{x_{2}-a}{b-a}=t$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{x_{1}-a}{b-a}=\frac{\frac{x_{2}-a}{b-a}}{\frac{x_{1}-a}{b-a}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $t=\frac{1-t}{t}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
最后的
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1}=\frac{-1+\sqrt{5}}{2}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $t_{2}=\frac{-1-\sqrt{5}}{2}$
\end_inset

, 取
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1}$
\end_inset

.这就是黄金分割常数,用
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

表示.
\end_layout

