\begin_layout Standard
设 
\begin_inset Formula $d=x+y$
\end_inset

, 则
\begin_inset Formula $k-z^{3}=d(x^{2}-xy+y^{2})$
\end_inset

 即: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(k-z^{3})\div d=x^{2}-xy+y^{2}
\]

\end_inset

由于
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}-xy+y^{2}$
\end_inset

是整数, 所以只需要保证
\begin_inset Formula $(k-z^{3})$
\end_inset

能够被d整除.
 即: 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

除以
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

的余数是z³
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
k\equiv z^{3}(\mod d)
\]

\end_inset


